---
import ServicePage from '../layouts/ServicePage.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What is a butt strip wax?",
    answer: "A butt strip wax (also called a butt crack wax or intergluteal wax) removes hair from the buttock crease area. It's a popular add-on to Brazilian waxing for complete smoothness."
  },
  {
    question: "Does butt strip waxing hurt?",
    answer: "While this area is sensitive, the treatment is quick and our experienced estheticians use techniques to minimize discomfort. Most clients find the results well worth the brief sensation."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does butt strip waxing last?",
    answer: "Results typically last 4-6 weeks, similar to Brazilian waxing. Many clients schedule this service together with their Brazilian wax for complete smoothness."
  }
];
---

<ServicePage
  title="Butt Strip Wax Phoenix | Butt Crack Waxing"
  description="Professional butt strip waxing in Phoenix, AZ. Complete your Brazilian wax with a butt crack wax for total smoothness. Discreet and professional. Book today!"
  price="$25"
  duration="10-15 min"
  location="phoenix"
  faqs={faqs}
>

<!-- Hero Image -->
<div class="mb-8">
  <img 
    src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_16da6a34-b6ce-4108-ba29-b3efd83e74d6_benefits-of-butt-wax.jpeg"
    alt="Butt strip waxing service at Rejuvenate You in Phoenix"
    class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover rounded-xl"
  />
</div>

<p class="text-lg mb-6">
  Complete your Brazilian wax with our butt strip waxing service. This treatment removes unwanted hair from the buttock crease area, giving you total smoothness and confidence from every angle.
</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">What is a Butt Strip Wax?</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
  <div>
    <img 
      src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_butt-strip-wax-service.jpg"
      alt="Butt strip wax service"
      class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="mb-4">
      A butt strip wax (also called intergluteal waxing) targets the area between the buttocks. It's the perfect add-on service for those who want:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
      <li>Complete smoothness with their Brazilian wax</li>
      <li>Confidence at the beach or pool</li>
      <li>Clean, hygienic feeling</li>
      <li>Longer-lasting results than shaving</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Popular Combination</h2>

<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <p class="mb-4">
    Most clients combine butt strip waxing with their <a href="/brazilian-wax-phoenix" style="color: #7B2D8E;" class="font-semibold hover:underline">Brazilian wax</a> for complete hair removal in the bikini area. This combination ensures you're smooth and confident from every angle.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can also add this service to a <a href="/bikini-wax-phoenix" style="color: #7B2D8E;" class="font-semibold hover:underline">bikini wax</a> for extended smoothness beyond the standard bikini line.
  </p>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">The Process</h2>

<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <ol class="space-y-4">
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">1.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Consultation</strong> — We discuss your comfort level and explain the process.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">2.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Preparation</strong> — The area is cleansed and prepped for optimal results.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">3.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Application</strong> — Gentle hard wax is applied to the targeted area.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">4.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Removal</strong> — Quick, professional removal for smooth results.
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Discreet and Professional</h2>

<p class="mb-6">
  Our experienced estheticians perform this service with the utmost professionalism and discretion. Your comfort is our priority, and we ensure a respectful, comfortable environment throughout your treatment.
</p>

