<p class="text-lg">
  Complete your waxing routine. <a href="https://app.squareup.com/appointments/book/e9ycxyisf79aby/L96KEQZQVHJ37/start" style="color: #7B2D8E;" class="font-semibold hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Book your butt strip waxing appointment</a> at our Phoenix location today! Only $25 for total smoothness and confidence.
</p>

</ServicePage>
